data.description: This beautiful spacious home has it all!! Around 2700 square feet (mol) of living space including 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, a big living area and formal dining room. Entertaining will be a breeze with the huge 20x40 back patio with custom shades, wired for a hot tub, & patio TV stays. Float around all summer in the 18x36 Inground pool, all one level which is perfect for sports, volleyball net stays. Serene rock water fall & pond next to the pool (winterized right now). Store all the pool equipment and floaties in the cabana house, which includes a full bathroom & shower, so no wet floors in the house! Listen to your favorite tunes with the surround sound system, speakers on the patio, primary bedroom, and living room (includes receiver, controlled by an app on your phone).  Primary bedroom is on it's own side of the house. The en suite bathroom is like a trip to the spa with heated tile floors, huge jetted bathtub, steam sauna shower, 2 separate vanities, & walk in closet. Kitchen features stainless steel appliances, double ovens, granite counter tops, abundance of cabinets, breakfast bar, pantry and dining nook. Fridge and brand new washer/dryer are negotiable. Seller is offering a $5000 flooring allowance with an acceptable offer to be used towards flooring of buyers choice. Features/updates: new water well pump 2020 (feeds the sprinkler system too), custom christmas lights with plugs installed and automatic timer, new 6' privacy wood fence with concrete footings 2019, sand filter for pool 2022, new pool liner 2021, guttering 2019, updated hot water heaters one on each side of the house, new roof on home and cabana house 2020, new windows 2017, new dual zoned heat and air units and new duct work 2019, french drains installed 2019 to assist with rain water runoff, new garage door & opener 2019 as well as new attic decking and insulation. In ground storm shelter in the garage. So many of the big ticket items have been done, pick out your new flooring and move right in!!
